question:
You have the following data (e.g., in JSON format):

```json
{
  "CustomerID": 1,
  "Name": "John Smith",
  "Contact": {
    "Email": "john@smith.com",
    "Phone": "555-555-5555"
  }
}
```

Which type of data is this?

